01:04:47.540 --> 01:04:49.429
JOHN: Shut up!

01:04:49.540 --> 01:04:51.542
(WIND CONTINUES WHISTLING)

01:04:53.660 --> 01:04:55.264
(SNIFFS)

01:04:55.380 --> 01:04:57.348
O.B.

01:04:59.620 --> 01:05:02.385
Do you know that nigger, sir?

01:05:02.500 --> 01:05:05.310
I don't know that nigger.

01:05:05.420 --> 01:05:09.823
But I know he's a nigger,
and that's all I need to know.

01:05:18.740 --> 01:05:20.185
CHRIS: Well...

01:05:20.300 --> 01:05:22.382
that nigger just ain't any nigger.

01:05:22.500 --> 01:05:23.945
That nigger, he...

01:05:24.060 --> 01:05:25.391
WARREN: General Sanford Smithers?

01:05:25.540 --> 01:05:27.907
Battle of Baton Rouge?

01:05:31.220 --> 01:05:36.024
Inform the nigger (CHUCKLING)
in the cavalry officer's uniform

01:05:36.140 --> 01:05:38.825
that I had a division of Confederates

01:05:38.940 --> 01:05:41.181
under my command...

01:05:41.300 --> 01:05:43.223
in Baton Rouge.

01:05:43.340 --> 01:05:46.071
Major Nigger, General Smithers
wishes me to inform you...

01:05:46.180 --> 01:05:48.751
I heard him, hillbilly.

01:05:48.860 --> 01:05:53.422
Inform this old cracker
that I was in Baton Rouge also.

01:05:53.540 --> 01:05:54.985
On the other side.

01:05:55.100 --> 01:05:56.465
(WIND RUSHING)

01:05:56.580 --> 01:05:58.469
Oh, that's interesting.

01:05:58.580 --> 01:06:00.423
Uh, General Smithers,

01:06:00.540 --> 01:06:03.544
he said that he was also in
Baton Rouge on the other si...

01:06:03.700 --> 01:06:07.143
Captain Mannix, tell the nigger

01:06:07.260 --> 01:06:09.627
that I don't acknowledge niggers

01:06:09.740 --> 01:06:11.265
in Northern uniforms.

01:06:11.420 --> 01:06:13.263
WARREN: You captured a whole colored command

01:06:13.420 --> 01:06:15.070
that day...

01:06:15.180 --> 01:06:18.468
but not one colored trooper
made it to a camp, did they?

01:06:18.580 --> 01:06:20.947
We didn't have the time or the food...

01:06:21.060 --> 01:06:24.143
nor the inclination...

01:06:24.260 --> 01:06:26.627
to care for Northern horses

01:06:26.740 --> 01:06:28.947
and least of all...

01:06:29.100 --> 01:06:31.068
Northern niggers!

01:06:31.180 --> 01:06:32.784
So we shot 'em where they stood!

01:06:32.940 --> 01:06:35.307
OSWALDO: Gentlemen.

01:06:35.420 --> 01:06:38.344
Gentlemen.

